- [Scheduler](scheduler.html)
- [Store](store.html)
- [Source Resolver](source-resolver.html)
- [Module Manifests](module-manifests.html)

2. Scope
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This reference explains the runtime model and public host-facing concepts. It does not document every internal Rust type.

Use this section when you need to understand how config, hosts, contexts, capabilities, and program execution fit together.
